node.text: Eric brought in his gorgeous 2016 Arancio Argos Huracan in for the SheepeyRace treatment. We added our Stage 1 SR 888-R kit to this car and made a very fun and streetable 800 hp. We couldn't be happier with the way this build turned out and neither can Eric.

node.text:
Looking to add another Tech/Installer to our company. Looking for the following.
- Experience
- Must be mechanically Inclined
- Must live locally or an acceptable driving distance 
- Quick Learner
- Attention to Detail
- VAG experience not required
If you are interested click the link in our bio and fill out the online form. Do not call, DM or show up in person. If there are issues filling out the form email career@sheepeyrace.com directly.
